<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.1.10">
<l>kalaiyulā valkul kārikai tiṟattuk kaṭalperum paṭaiyoṭuñ ceṉṟu</l>
<l>cilaiyiṉā lilaṅkai tīyeḻac ceṟṟa tirukkaṇṇaṅ kuṭiyuṇiṉ ṟāṉai</l>
<l>malaikulā māṭa maṅkaiyar talaivaṉ māṉavēl kaliyaṉvā yolikaḷ</l>
<l>ulavucol mālai yoṉpatō ṭoṉṟum vallavark killainal kuravē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For those who master this garland of words in nine-and-one [verses]</l>
<l rend="indent">in which poems progress [in a series]</l>
<l>Of Kaliyaṉ with a [well-]shaped spear, leader of those of Maṅkai</l>
<l rend="indent">with a raised shrine extolled as a mountain,</l>
<l>On the one who stands in Tirukkaṇṇaṅkuṭi</l>
<l rend="indent">who destroyed Laṅkā when he set [it] afire with his bow,</l>
<l>Arriving with a great army [like] an ocean, for the sake of the beauty</l>
<l rend="indent">on whose hips a girdle swayed, there will be no poverty.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
